<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ900928-0089</DOCNO><DOCID>900928-0089.</DOCID><HL>   Who's News:   Sony Corp.</HL><DATE>09/28/90</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION</SO><CO>   SNE WNEWS</CO><IN>HOME ELECTRONICS, FURNISHINGS, APPLIANCES (HMF)</IN><LP>   SONY Corp. (Tokyo) -- Abbott L. Brown was named executivevice president and chief financial officer of ColumbiaPictures Entertainment Inc., a Los Angeles-based subsidiaryof this international electronics concern. Mr. Brown, whoalso will be named to the Columbia board, succeeds LarryRuisi, who continues as an executive vice president. Mr.Brown was previously the Southern California group managingpartner at Price Waterhouse, the accounting firm. PriceWaterhouse separately announced that L. Dale Crandallsucceeds Mr. Brown. Previously, he was managing partner ofthe firm's San Francisco office.</LP><TEXT/></DOC>